      "message": "\u003e iiuc, this is specific to the RM, so you can just create it inside runimpl.New(), passing a context if necessary\n\u003e (prior art: PM creates Gerrit poller)\n\nCorrect and this is exactly how my initial implementation looks like. I think I didn\u0027t end up doing that because `tree.Client` has different implementation for prod and test. One is `tree.NewClient(..)` and the other one is `treetest.NewFake(..).Client()`. So it has to be initialized differently at top level (see here and e2e test) and pass it down to RM.\n\nI\u0027m actually thinking of using https://golang.org/pkg/net/http/httptest/#Server.Start to start a test server to fake tree so that there doesn\u0027t need to be a separate test implementation for tree.Client and all tests are really exercising the real prod code path. WDYT?",
